subject: Nascar Nextel Cup Series
Automobiles
Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Sunday’s Nascar Nextel Cup race at Phoenix International Raceway will be the 16th and final event of 2007 for the big, boxy Car of Tomorrow, which will be used for the entire 36-race schedule next year.
